 "remarks": "Experience modern luxury in this beautifully reimagined home, set on 1.57 scenic, park-like acres. Thoughtfully renovated, this 2,864 sq ft residence offers open-concept living spaces filled with natural light and sophisticated finishes throughout.   The designer kitchen features a stunning island and premium cabinetry, flowing seamlessly into the dining and living areas with a dramatic linear fireplace.   The spacious family room opens to a sun-soaked bluestone patio overlooking an expansive backyard extending to the pond-an idyllic setting for entertaining and everyday enjoyment. The fabulous primary suite is a private retreat with a cozy fireplace, incredible walk-in closet, and beautifully appointed modern bath.   Two additional bedrooms complete the second level, while a private 4th-bedroom ensuite is ideal for guests or flexible living space. A main-level office/5th bedroom, powder room, and mudroom with custom built-ins leading to the 2-car garage add versatility and convenience.   Ideally located within walking distance of Staples High School and Bedford Middle School, and minutes from Westport&apos;s beaches, vibrant downtown, shopping, dining, and train station.",
